Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是关于桃太郎的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开传说之谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬 雉 猿 还有鬼的登场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩  头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是  名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.10,0:02:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把系在腰上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄米团子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.10,0:02:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.90,0:02:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前传说《桃太郎》的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.70,0:02:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是7世纪中叶从国外飞来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无比残暴的恶鬼 温罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和当时被朝廷派遣去打倒他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武勇无双的战士 吉备津彦命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者间战斗的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而事实却并非如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.30,0:02:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上公元663年《日本书记》有关这段历史的记载是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.10,0:02:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在白村江之战大败后逃回日本的大和军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.00,0:02:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}{\pos(320,370)}[鬼之城]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防备对手的攻击不断修筑了众多的关隘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼之城就是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说该城堡似乎就位于
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.80,0:02:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本建有城池的冈山县吉备津一带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.10,0:02:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉备路有众多古坟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.10,0:03:00.50,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,30)}注:蝙蝠冢古坟 作山古坟 造山古坟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问 在这些遗迹里一定保留着那个时期的文化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和当时人们各式各样的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.30,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}{\pos(320,370)}[冈山县立吉备路乡土馆]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.20,0:03:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃太郎解谜之旅（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到冈山  首先想到的当然就是桃太郎了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到桃太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄米团子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太就知道吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.80,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬和雉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.00,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有猿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鬼岛 打败恶鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.60,0:03:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得倒是没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这可是千载难逢的还可以学习历史的周末旅行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛  我还特意准备了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就稍微说点专业的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是先就着这里特产的青鳞鱼来喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.40,0:03:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  连博士都这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈山 冈山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到冈山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要换乘山阳本线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么着急嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车已经靠站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.00,0:04:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓敷最有名的就是历史风貌区的白墙街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}{\pos(320,370)}[仓敷站 北口]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿可是喜爱旅行的女孩子梦想中的地方哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.00,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  在此之前我其实更想到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.10,0:04:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.50,0:04:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[仓敷Tivoli公园]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起Tivoli主题公园…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧 圣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有资格说这些吗 猿渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.80,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我帮你在新闻上宣传 你现在能独立吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经为这个不知付了多少钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来还想看在同学份上给你打个折呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.80,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对步美都干了些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而打扰你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里话 是我们太不稳重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用连我们也请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没这么想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩给人家道歉了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.80,0:05:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.70,0:06:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹 我们请的冰激凌好吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.60,0:06:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你这么道歉的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥你们是朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架可不好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的确是小学的同班同学 不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有人去了东京和大阪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是分开15年后的再会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.50,0:06:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家成年以后第一次相见呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 是同学会吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.50,0:06:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了说了 我是阿笠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.60,0:06:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道该说是领着这些孩子还是跟着这些孩子来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.60,0:06:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是步美 吉田步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名叫圆谷光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小岛元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是江户川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是 少年侦探团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是郑重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是桃井直人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是木岛弥生 多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几位是 猿渡健吾  
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾圣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼贯守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年侦探团啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我们也有过类似这样的组名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这次我们为了什么聚会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.80,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来说吧 本来这就是我出的主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次是为了声援桃井君的选举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及祝贺他和弥生结婚而发起的聚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 参加选举啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有结婚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.20,0:07:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是桃太郎和雉小姐的结合呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彦也发现了吗 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.10,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥你们是“桃太郎”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为名字吧 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的名字开头的两个假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是在《桃太郎》里出场的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.90,0:07:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃 雉 猿 犬 鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是少年侦探团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.80,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我们就是因为各自的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还曾经在学艺会上演过《桃太郎》呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少年以前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怀念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.80,0:08:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那时的剧本和导演真的很不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是俊也负责的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要提了 都是过去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 待会儿做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想过了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去寻宝如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭的时候再给你们解释吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.70,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 在此之前都是自由活动时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们也出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[仓敷历史风貌区]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是仓敷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里保存了江户时代街道的旧貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.50,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 几乎都是当时的商人们所建造的仓库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.10,0:09:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这条仓敷河上用船运送过各种各样的商品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.20,0:09:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座仓敷考古馆东侧的外墙砖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}{\pos(320,370)}[仓敷考古馆]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.60,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个历史风貌区最美的景色之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里收集了以仓敷为首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.70,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉备 濑户内海沿岸一带从古墓和遗址中出土的文物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学到了不少东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以接触到古时候的文化啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以学到不少东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 果然还是这个最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是青鳞鱼最好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.90,0:09:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪有人说就算是借钱也想要吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是为了这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.50,0:09:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是桃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃太郎的桃子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道不是真的桃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 里边装的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些信封是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里边装的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.00,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是暗号 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是暗号 也没什么难的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学水平而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.50,0:10:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这可是只有在这里才能学到的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.90,0:10:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开暗号  发掘古墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成能找到鬼岛的宝藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开桃太郎的传说哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们干吧 我们干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.00,0:10:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我在附近休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给你了 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是博士你搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.90,0:10:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不知道 不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习首先要有兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.90,0:10:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 能找到适合的教材真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.00,0:10:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.90,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年侦探团 寻宝开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这画的是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛 这是睫毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是火吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想也很正常啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火和眼睛是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火 眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火和眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火和眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是防火了望塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}{\pos(320,370)}[防火了望塔]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到什么没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到什么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宝藏哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打开 快打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.40,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 都是些乱七八糟的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.40,0:12:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电池没电了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不是什么宝藏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那6年真的很快乐 如果除开那件事的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事指的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.50,0:12:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这个是时间胶囊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间胶囊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.70,0:12:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是人家的时间胶囊的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把它挖出来这不大好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.20,0:12:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  在我们之前的确有人把它挖出来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.70,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.10,0:12:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寻宝的竞争者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.50,0:12:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样那我们千万不能输啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把下一个暗号解开吧  柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画了房间的这张画上的字母是PIBTIJ吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  一点都看不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.90,0:13:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是最基础的暗号哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.20,0:13:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些字母的前一位找出来再连在一起看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 P的前边是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O啊 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.10,0:13:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来I的前边 是H吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OHASHI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吃饭时用的筷子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 大概是指地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就在这仓敷周围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才的大姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在解暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐你在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在单独行动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被大家讨厌了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你们不是看到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你们不是同班同学吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从不会撒谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时要写鬼贯公司的宣传报道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就写了篇《高利贷的台前幕后》的文章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.80,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿渡独立开美容院的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也如实地报道了他的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是很蹩脚啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.80,0:14:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有弥生 和桃井的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.80,0:14:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他前不久都还在交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.80,0:14:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  所以才会和他们发生摩擦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位叫俊也先生的他没来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.70,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感觉敏锐的名侦探呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.50,0:14:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎听说大姐姐你们曾经出演的《桃太郎》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他担当的编剧兼导演啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会叫他来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他还活着的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他过世了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.80,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在15年前的一场交通事故中啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我们没能一同毕业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.60,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.40,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个正义感很强的 很不错的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.90,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  伤感起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.80,0:15:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦  少年侦探团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.90,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OHASHI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OHSHI 大桥别墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么感觉跟古装剧一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 这家叫大桥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.50,0:15:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前因为开发盐田后来当了大地主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.70,0:15:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些建筑 似乎也经历了200年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.20,0:15:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 过奖了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前准备过真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样 在我们之前被挖出来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧漫画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有旧文具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.90,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸上写着:那件事真是让我大吃一惊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是“那件事”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.90,0:15:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要赶在他前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  下一个下一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方形的小丑的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.30,0:15:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫什么来着  就是手机上用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是象形文字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.10,0:16:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个小写的t 这是u 然后又是t
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  似乎是个a
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是反的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tuta  常春藤吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常春藤 是那种植物吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常春藤在英语里是Ivy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方形的意思是广场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那儿 是那儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.20,0:16:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓敷常春藤广场啊 就是这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.20,0:16:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}{\pos(320,370)}[仓敷常春藤广场]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是常春藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.00,0:16:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好宽敞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里以前是纺织工厂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还在使用原来的建筑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建成旅馆和纪念馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.40,0:16:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 快开始找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没那样的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.40,0:17:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上边反着写的不光是a
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是反的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  这个常春藤广场的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 是后面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到宝藏了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.00,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸上写着:那件事…不大对劲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这些啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人大失所望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个大姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  已经没呼吸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O N I  鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是鬼  是桃太郎里的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是发现者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是少年侦探团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果犯人是鬼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是桃太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要制服 不对 要逮捕他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 那是被害者的物品吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个邮戳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么盖反了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.10,0:18:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是被害者的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那4个人马上就接受了调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.00,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说大家都没有不在场证明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确地说是一个人独处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.50,0:18:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过Tivoli公园里有很多游客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有人还记得我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.70,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在旅社前的大厅里也有很多人在场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.40,0:19:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很遗憾啊 要确认是很困难的 两位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该没什么问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人一直都在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在历史风貌区散步是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.80,0:19:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我们一直在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.10,0:19:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分开也就只有上洗手间的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此 那也只不过是5分钟而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.70,0:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 已订婚的人的证词是不能被采纳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.60,0:19:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且根据调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说你以前曾和被害者交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.40,0:19:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外的两位听说也和被害者有些摩擦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津山警官 人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是桃形的盒子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.90,0:19:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是和案件没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为了保险起见我们想最好还是让警官先生看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就和您联系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们很不情愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.10,0:19:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是搜查是一定要全力协助的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  莫非是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.90,0:19:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是装入了我们时间胶囊的暗号的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人吃惊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  这暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.80,0:20:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他们为了表示15年前时间胶囊埋藏地点的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.70,0:20:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年前5个人把装有充满回忆的物品的时间胶囊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互交换混在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.90,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自埋下了别人的时间胶囊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.70,0:20:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了不让自己知道自己的盒子埋在了哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.10,0:20:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许才会留下当时真正的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.20,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上 昨晚有人闯入了大家毕业的小学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.40,0:20:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盗的物品中 已经查明有这个盒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.40,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 是他们拣到后和我们联络的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.10,0:20:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和你们很有缘嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么会偷那样的东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正是因为明白它不值一文以后 就被扔掉了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.20,0:20:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么会不会是这样 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.90,0:20:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣子作为记者想阻止那个闯入学校的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而被害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.80,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.00,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有不同的看法 鬼贯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.40,0:21:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.40,0:21:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你只是重要的参考人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.50,0:21:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只留下我一个不是很奇怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.70,0:21:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么解释这个死亡讯息呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.60,0:21:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是因为被害人写的新闻而对她心存恨意吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是守吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.70,0:21:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 猿渡君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连桃井君也这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现在这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁杀了谁都没什么奇怪的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.10,0:21:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候也不会去寻宝了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}{\pos(320,370)}[仓敷大酒店]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.90,0:21:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人果然是鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.60,0:21:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真想抓住犯人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.80,0:21:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的元太  都是因为你拿反了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.60,0:22:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手拿刀  左手拿叉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.20,0:22:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦啊  我习惯用右手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想用右手拿叉子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.70,0:22:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要筷子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你一开始的时候干嘛不说啊  博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是这么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.80,0:22:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话死亡讯息的内容就变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.80,0:22:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就有信心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人在那4人之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.60,0:22:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要找出他还要解开剩下的两个暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.60,0:22:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到埋藏的时间胶囊才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.60,0:24:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你挖出了时间胶囊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.90,0:24:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么做那样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.00,0:24:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有要调查的东西 一个人去了书店和图书馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.30,0:24:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道会有这样的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.30,0:24:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我圆谷光彦都记下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.60,0:24:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.70,0:24:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 光彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.10,0:24:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.50,0:24:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃太郎解谜之旅（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.30,0:24:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.50,0:24:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左撇子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.50,0:24:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次抓住那个鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.60,0:24:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊  柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.70,0:24:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是从竹子里面…